Qt (Widgets)
https://www.qt.io/
License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0

  Qt is dynamically linked via OBS Studio dependencies; AunSync does not
  redistribute the Qt libraries. See https://doc.qt.io/qt-6/lgpl.html for
  details.

========================================================================

FFmpeg
https://ffmpeg.org/
License: GNU General Public License v2.0 or later

  AunSync does not bundle or link FFmpeg. For OBS broadcast (RTSP E2E)
  latency measurement, the plugin can download an FFmpeg executable at
  runtime from the BtbN FFmpeg-Builds project
  (https://github.com/BtbN/FFmpeg-Builds) and invokes it as a separate
  process. The downloaded "win64-gpl" build is distributed under the GPL.
  See https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html for details.
